Title: Kent & Stowe 70100476 Traditional Bypass Secateurs K/S70100476
Description:
Kent & Stowe Traditional Bypass Secateurs for cutting delicate stems, a bypass action is less likely to cause bruising to the stem. Ideal for use on roses, shrubs and general pruning of green, live wood.

Drop forged for strength and durability. The precision ground, carbon steel blades have a non-stick coating. Not for use on dead wood as this will blunt the blades.

Specification

Cutting Diameter: 18mm
Length: 200mm (8in)
Guarantee: 5 years
